                      <locus target="#iv(erso) #iir(ecto)"/>" Asmat Prayer of David for a person bitten by a snake,
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ ለዘነደፎ፡ አርዌ፡ ምድር።</foreign>, written in pencil.
