                      <desc>
                      Navigation system:
                      orange yarn is sewn into the fore edge of <locus target="#1"/>;
                      maroon yarn is sewn into the fore edge of <locus target="#7"/>;
                      white yarn is sewn into the fore edge of <locus target="#14"/>.
                    </desc>
