                      <desc>
                      Scribal intervention:
                      words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#16v #17r #35v #41r #47v"/>, etc.);
                      and lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#19r #54r #58v #86v #94r"/>, etc.);
                      and in the upper margin with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (<locus target="#157v"/>, col. 1, line 4); erasure markings are visible (<locus target="#135v"/>);
                      text has been removed (<locus target="#30v #53v #69r #75v #87v"/>, etc.)
                    </desc>
